Class CircularLinkedList

java.lang.Object
util.CircularLinkedList
public class CircularLinkedList extends Object
Represents a circular linked list that stores Technician objects. This data structure allows for efficient insertion, deletion, and traversal of Technician nodes.
Author:
Dhawal Arora (Netid: da812)
